  <h2>Switch Buttons</h2>

  <p>Take a regular <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code> of links and add <code>.nav-tabs</code>:</p>


  <div class="dive-docs-example">
    <input type="checkbox" id="switch-main" class="switch-checkbox" />
    <label class="switch" for="switch-main">
      <div class="switch-slider">
        <div class="switch-button">&nbsp;</div>
        <div class="switch-content switch-content--left"><span>ON</span></div>
        <div class="switch-content switch-content--right"><span>OFF</span></div>
      </div>
    </label>
  </div>
