  <h3>BEWARE!</h3>
  <p><strong>IMPORTANT:</strong> the <code>id=""</code> of the <code>&lt;input&gt;</code>  must match the <code>for=""</code> attribute of the <code>&lt;label&gt;</code>. So if you have multiple Switch buttons on a single page, each must have a unique <code>id</code> and <code>for</code> attribute.</p>

  <p><strong>Also:</strong> the markup has to be structured exactly how it is structured in the example.  The <code>&lt;input&gt;</code> must immediately precede the <code>&lt;label&gt;</code> otherwise it will not work.</p>

  <h2>Switch Sizes</h2>
